Chapter 4:<br>
<br>
        Hung's eyes opened. He squinted but could not see more than a blur. His eyes began to focus in on his surroundings. He was in some sort of garage. Men dressed in black holding machine guns were everywhere. He heard his partners behind him. They were untied.<br>
&quot;Guys, cut my rope.&quot; Hung said, shaking his head. They laughed as they were enjoying it. &quot;Guys, what are ya'll doing?&quot; <br>
&quot;Oh Jon, i guess you can't take a hint.&quot; Law said.&quot;lets just say me and Lang got paid to work for the biggest assasin in the United States of America. Hung shook his head in confusment.<br>
&quot;You mean....&quot; Hung began.<br>
&quot;Surprise, &quot;Lang said.<br>
&quot;I trusted you with my all.&quot; Hung said in an angry voice.<br>
&quot;I know.&quot; Law said laughing. <br>
&quot;But your leg.&quot; Hung said looking down. <br>
&quot;Oh please that was just a blank and the blood was cornsyrup.&quot; Law laughed.<br>
&quot;Glad you could make it.&quot; a voice said behind him. It was Timothey Hanley. <br>
&quot;You see,&quot;Lang began.&quot;Our friend Hanley is the &quot;Big Time Assasin&quot; you have been looking for.&quot;<br>
&quot;It is amazing how much a little face paint and fake facial hair with change your whole appearence.&quot; Hanley said. Hung shook his head in disbelife of what was happening.<br>
&quot;Let me explain.&quot; Hanley said.&quot;A fairly long time ago, you started coming on to me. So i decided I was going to cancel you for good. I waited until you were in a public place. I belive it was a park of somesort. Oh well I don't remember. But just as I pulled the trigger, your wife skipped right in the way. I was then going to kill you but decided your wife's death would be enough to keep you down for a little while. After that I went to your two partners and offered them ten-thousand to work for me. So you see it looks like you were alone the whole time.&quot; Hung began to pull away at the ducktape around his wrist. He twisted it until one hand was free. He acted like he was still tied up to the chair. <br>
&quot;Sorry but now you gotta die.&quot; Law said smiling and holding up his pistol. Hung threw his hands around hard choping at Law's arm in two different directions causing it to break. His pistol fell and Hung caught it. Raising it up he shot Law twice in the chest. Hanley began to run. Hung ran and jumped behind a metal rack. Bullets from the machine guns ricoched around the large building. <br>
&quot;Stop, you idiots.&quot; Lang said walking to where Hung was.&quot;bullets bouce off of metal, you wanna kill us all.&quot; Hung jumped up and shot Lang twice in the head. Machine gun fire started again. Hung jumped up and shot twice at the men. One man fell. Hung ran aroud the huge rack standing next to him. He picked up one of the machine guns and began to fire into the crowd of men. They fired back. bullets whized by his head. He ducked down. He surveyed his room. On the shelf was a box filled with styfrofoam. He picked it up and threw it into the rain of gun fire. As it flew accross the room the men fired at it. Hung ran out, sliding across the floor he pulled his trigger causing all of the men to fall. He stood lup and ran to the direction which Hanley ran. Inside he was burning with hatered of the whole situation. Everyone was against him. He burst through the door and out into the night. The two buildings made it a bottleneck for him. He looked but could see no sign of Hanley. He began to walk down the path. A noise was heard behind him. Just as he turned he heard a bullet hit the ground by his feet. He quickley turned his head. Looking up on the rooftop of another building he saw Hanley with his rifle. He shot two rounds at him but missed. Hanley turned and began to run. Hung quickley surveyed his surounding. When he was a teenager he studied martial arts and learned to adapt to his surroundings. Hung ran his fastest. He ran kicking one wall and bouncing to the other and kicking himself to the roof. Hanley began down the stairs. Hung fired the machine gun but missed. He pursued after Hanley. Running down the stairs and into the street. No cars were in sight. Hanley turned around and fired his rifle catching Hung in the arm. Hung fired the machine gun hitting Hanley in the stomach. He fell to the ground. Hung walked over and kicked him in the side. A scream came out from Hanley.<br>
&quot;That was for my wife.&quot; Hung said. He aimed his gun at him.<br>
&quot;You can't shoot me. You have to take me in. It is against the Law.&quot; Hanley said laughing. Hung looked at him in the eyes and held the trigger down for a brief three seconds. &quot;I am the Law.&quot;<br>
